dct_description_sm: "For use by the War and Navy Department Agencies only. Not for sale or distribution." "Note: officers using this map will mark hereon corrections and additions which come to their attention and mail direct to the Chief of Engineers, Washington, D.C." Notes variation and annual change in magnetic and true north. Map shows railways, roads, public buildings, cemeteries, and Arab quarters. "4-43."
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : War Office. General Staff Geographical Section, 1943.
Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
